727598f-b.title: Queens: Northern Boulevard - 57th Street
727598f-b.text:
Northern Boulevard, north side, west from 58th to 57th Streets. View 2 shows the house at the N.E. corner of 57th Street. The inscription over the doorway reads: Tedeschi and Tedeschi, Designers, Manufacturers, Builders.
P. L. Sperr  August 24, 1935
NO REPRODUCTIONS  Views 1,2
